The Secret in Their Eyes;;93;;89;;R;;Hoping to put to rest years of unease concerning a past case, retired criminal investigator Benjamín Espósito (Ricardo Darín) begins writing a novel based on the decades-old unsolved mystery of a newlywed's rape and murder. With the help of a former colleague, Judge Irene Menéndez Hastings (Soledad Villamil), Benjamín attempts to make sense of the past. The journey through his memories sets Benjamín on a thrilling emotional path that leads to a shocking realization.;;Drama,Crime,Mystery & thriller;;Juan José Campanella;;2010;;Ricardo Darín,Soledad Villamil,Carla Quevedo,Pablo Rago,Javier Godino,Guillermo Francella,José Luis Gioia,Bárbara Palladino,Rudy Romano,Mario Alarcón,Alejandro Abelenda,Sebastián Blanco;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/secret_in_their_eyes